messages.messageBody:
**Sandra, having WAY much fun with that game!**

And thank goodness no one is telling you that it's time to get off the computer! How much joy would have been robbed from the rest of us :) That was really fun!

We've been big on the computer today, (putting in some info for the questions about computer use earlier today) playing Sandra's game, e-mailing different people, playing games. My daughter even drew up a graph to watch prices within the World of Warcraft. Amazing!

If you'd like to read about her venture into the world of economics, its at my blog today. :) And she also wrote about it at her blog.




Kelli~


http://ourjoyfullife.blogspot.com/

"Life shrinks or expands in proportion to one's courage." ~Anais Nin




---------------------------------
Pinpoint customers who are looking for what you sell.
